<h2>Other Links and Resources</h2>

<h3>Recent Workshops</h3>

<ul>
	<li><a href="http://clopinet.com/isabelle/Projects/AISTATS2010/">Active Learning and Experimental Design</a> (AISTATS 2010)</li>
	<li><a href="http://active-learning.net/alnlp2010/">Active Learning for NLP</a> (NAACL-HLT 2010)</li>
	<li><a href="http://www.dmargineantu.net/workshop/BudgetedLearning_ICML-2010/">Budgeted Learning Workshop</a> (ICML 2010)</li>
	<li><a href="http://users.isr.ist.utl.pt/~rmcantin/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/RSS10/RSS10">Towards Closing the Loop: Active Learning for Robotics</a> (RSS 2010)</li>
	<li><a href="https://facwiki.cs.byu.edu/nlp/index.php/Workshop_on_Active_Learning_for_NLP">Active Learning for NLP</a> (NAACL-HLT 2009)</li>
	<li><a href="http://users.isr.ist.utl.pt/~rmcantin/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/NIPS09/NIPS09">Adaptive Sensing, Active Learning, and Experimental Design</a> (NIPS 2009)</li>
	<li><a href="http://www.cs.iastate.edu/~oksayakh/cslworkshop_nips2008.html">Cost-Sensitive Learning</a> (NIPS 2008)</li>
</ul>

